{"type":"message","id":"ef66bcba","parentId":"4552d1f0","timestamp":"2026-05-03T17:02:42.172Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script ran successfully. It found 0 new conversations for Finn since the last heartbeat. This could mean either:\n1. No new sessions since last check\n2. Sessions were already logged\n3. State file is already tracking the most recent session\n\nThe script works as expected - it checks the last 3 sessions for the \"finn\" agent and logs any new ones. Since it returned 0, there were no new sessions to log since the last heartbeat.\n","thinkingSignature":"10cf9e514605c4de377466e4f3dbb41ebe914b66c51f5ef163119e626d0f1bb2"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nDone — the wiki heartbeat ran successfully for Finn. There were **0 new conversations** logged, meaning all recent sessions were already captured in the previous heartbeat run (or no new sessions have occurred since the last check).\n\nThe script tracks state in `memory-wiki/.heartbeat_logger_state.json` to avoid duplicate logging."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":162,"output":162,"cacheRead":17344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777827755873,"responseId":"0646b2abcba4241be03769344409ddc6"}}
